    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taat is a 2D family friendly sokoban-style puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic and newer puzzle games, taat brings the joy of solving puzzles to everyone!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Includes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute 2D pixel art visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appropriate soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different save slots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of puzzle mechanics including breaking walls, lasers, portals, traps and ... chickens!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quick manual</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game autosaves after each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial explains the controls and the details of the mechanics of some elements. It's recommended to leave it on for the first playthrough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chickens react consistently to obstacles (player, walls, boxes).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If a level looks hard, don't rush through it. Take some time to observe what is happening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement: Arrow keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player 2 Movement: W,A,S,D</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reset Level: Backspace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select menu item: Enter or Space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exit to main menu, go to previous menu item : ESC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon game completion, Jump to previous/next level: Comma (,) and Period (.) respectively</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement: Pad, Left analog stick</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reset Level: Y</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select menu item: A</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exit to main menu, go to previous menu item : B</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon game completion, Jump to previous/next level: Shoulder Buttons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using Steam Input is recommended</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
